{"tid":2064602,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[現場bid] 10組客排隊搶樓 放盤1日","createTime":"2020-06-15T02:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T05:36:59.000Z","uid":73269,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bfc62b34db9e8c8357cf49deccd228ec868463","tid":2064602,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[現場bid] </span></span><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情漸漸緩和，一、二手樓市交投回升，優質單位吸引買家爭搶。市場消息透露，沙田好運中心錄椰林閣低層E室，實用面積348平方呎，兩房間隔，座向西南，由於業主剛為單位全屋翻新裝修，而且叫價僅515萬放盤，屬於市場最平叫單位，故昨日吸引逾10組客人排隊等睇樓，故單位放盤僅1天，即以548萬元沽出，較業主開價搶貴33萬元。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，同座一個僅低1層的E室，今年3月以約453萬元售出，兩者相差1層售價相差95萬元。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產高級分行經理卜穎芝表示，上述單位原業主於2013年2月以340萬元購入單位，持貨7年，是次沽出單位賬面獲利208萬元離場，單位期內升值61%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/747c8e/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_200615/20200615_60410f12e9e3424ba128gKbhudZzH0qH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F747c8e%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_200615%2F20200615_60410f12e9e3424ba128gKbhudZzH0qH.jpg&h=2b7ab382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/158517/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_200614/20200614_42cd819f06bce169c739w7ojYrqxoVQO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F158517%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_200614%2F20200614_42cd819f06bce169c739w7ojYrqxoVQO.jpg&h=9b3bb57e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2669862?r=cpstni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2669862%3Fr%3Dcpstni&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8m9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=28bfc55a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2669862?r=cpstni</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6b8440/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/